name: Corneo's Mercy (Overwatch) Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Mercy (Angela Ziegler) from Overwatch. Use corneo_mercy to activate.

You can produce images without Mercy's signature wings and/or halo if desired. Things like mechanical_wings and glowing_wings in the negative prompt help.

Version 2 images produced with my 7th Heaven Mix available here https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!

modelVersions.description:
I discovered a bug in one of the tools used in my textual inversion training process, which actually means everything released so far is not as accurate as it could have been! This explains why the eyes and other features were sometimes so bad. The flip side of this is now I'm struggling with overbaking the new versions, so I'm still learning how to improve on these but I believe these v2 versions (more to follow for the other released embeddings) are an improvement over the original. Will also stop Mercy having that double ponytail she sometimes had on v1!

I've included some comparison shots to show the difference
